1:13 PM Defendant Alicia M Johnson appeared by video, in custody.   Prosecuting attorney Brian H. Wright Aty in court for the State of Wisconsin. Attorney Kaitlin Elizabeth Dippolito appeared by video for Alicia M Johnson, for today.
